milestones.description: Javed Miandad has broken the record for most ODIs (7) as captain for PAK, going past Asif Iqbal
This is the lowest match aggregate (378) involving teams Australia & Pakistan in ODIs
Javed Miandad has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (23) for PAK, going past Wasim Raja
Tahir Naqqash and Ashraf Ali's 32-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 30 between Wasim Bari and Imran Khan
